data.title: Mixing & Mastering Engineers, Producers & Songwriters who worked with Wiz Khalifa
data.meta_description: Sound engineers who have worked with Wiz Khalifa - Read Reviews, Listen to Samples, Search by Budget, Credits, Genre and more. Matt Foster, Jimmy Deer...
data.text:
CREDITS: Maxim/The Prodigy, Ludacris,Wiz Khalifa,The Yeah Yeah Yeahs,Gorillaz,Swedish House Mafia,Baddies Only,Kelis,Sean Paul,Sugababes,Ms Dynamite,Nadia Rose. Trained and then worked in top London studios for 20+ years (Miloco, StrongRoom, Townhouse) / Advanced Mixing Course tutor for 10 years at The London School of Sound.

I have worked on Billboard #1s with Grammy/Platinum artists + writers–Seal, Wiz Khalifa, Juicy J, Gorillaz' Miho Hatori, Blac Youngsta, India.Arie and more–garnering millions of streams + over 300 major label, film+tv placements in the process. I'll bring all this experience and passion to your project. I love to teach too!

Hooks? Demos? Mixing? Writing? Post Production? Lets work. Im a multi platinum Artist, Producer, and Writer and Mixer ( BTS, Chainsmokers , Ty Dolla Sign, Chris Brown ,Kacey Musgraves, Jeremih, and many more) ( Madden , NBA 2k, UFC, Insecure (HBO) , Space Jam, more). Wide vocal and production range . Can do any genre for male or female.

| Unlimited Free Revisions | MixedByIcon, also known as Icon or Jaycen Joshua Jr. , is a world-renowned go-to mixer for the Current Tastemakers in music He has worked with multitudes of Artists over the past decade from independent Artists to mainstream Artists. LET'S WORK TODAY!

Credits with Demi Lovato, Selena Gomez and more. When I start a project big or small, it’s always about the song. I do whatever I can to let the song be the best it can be. I let the essence of the song take the forefront. I have passion, patience and determination to bring out the very best in every project I work on.

I specialise in combining timeless pop sensibilities with alternative and eclectic flavours, to bring out the unique elements in every mix. With tricks and techniques learnt from Paul Epworth, Mark Ronson and Ben Baptie, I'm ready to elevate your tracks so they reach their full potential!

I am a Grammy nominated music producer and artist, best known as one half of independent soul duo The Foreign Exchange from North Carolina. I have over two decades of experience as a recording and performing artist, music producer and mixer, remixer and (film) composer, garnering hundreds of thousands of sales and millions of streams.

I am a Grammy Award trumpeter that has a unique style of playing on hip hop, jazz, pop, blues, and just about any style of music. I have a lot of credits with my style of trumpet playing. I received a Grammy for playing on Usher album She Dont Know. Please check my blog at www.darnelltrumpetdudephillips.blogspot.com

My goal is to make every song be the best that it can be. Music is my life and I take pride in my work. I have years of experience working with talented artist. Mixing, mastering and producing. I find my hands in just about all aspects of the music creation process.

Hey guys, JackEL here. I've been professionally producing music for 10 years, and have done Singles for 2 Chainz, Lana Del Ray, The Weekend, Stevie Wonder, Beenie Man + More. I've done remixes for Linkin Park & Christina Aguilera. I've Ghost Produced for Wiz Khalifa, Three Six Mafia, and various other Grammy Winning artists.

I am a multi-genre producer, mixing/mastering engineer, and multi-instrumentalist. My focus is on Pop, Hip-Hop, R&B, and EDM. I also do voice acting and copy-reading. My credits include Akon, Jim Jones, Wiz Khalifa, T.I., Paul Wall, 2 Chainz, Gucci Mane, Brotha Lynch Hung, Syren, Tallboi Ent., Seanessy, Good Ol’ Boyz, and many more.

I'm all about the song! I pride myself on my ability to connect with a feeling and translate that into memorable melodies and powerful lyrics. Songwriting is my passion and I have been blessed enough to make it into a career.

A Sound Engineer who has worked with from the world "Wiz Khalifa, 6ix9ine, Snoop Dogg, The Game, Gucci Mane, Eko Fresh" from Turkey "Ceza, Sefo, Yalın, Bilal Sonses, Reynmen" and more than 500 different artists in total.

I'm a professional Artist, Songwriter in the Bay Area. Best known work for LoveRance’s UP! I have worked & performed with E-40, 50 Cent, Wiz Khalifa, Kehlani and More. As a versatile artist, I believe I can make your song sound the way you have been picturing it. Currently have a New song out with IAMSU & ShowBanga titled. "Too Cocky”

The tone is in your touch. This has been my guiding principle as a player and producer since day one. Specializing in bringing mojo, sauce, and depth to your track, my 20 years of sonic obsession, dedication and debt are definitive of my work. If asked to describe what i do across all genres i have done in one word, it would be "QuietLOUD"

Quality is everything. Producing quality work will always be something I take pride in. I do everything from songwriting, production, mixing, mastering, and engineering. Understanding the importance of a decent turnaround, and client satisfaction, I've always stood on worthy work.

Glashaus boasts over 1.3 billion streams, with production and engineering credits including icons like Billy Joel, Selena Gomez, and Post Malone. Our Hollywood-based studio specializes in delivering top-tier production, mixing, mastering, and customized vocal packages, setting the standard for excellence in the music industry.

Augustyn Engty is an Indian artist. set to create a good artworks around the artworld. he was born in 15, august, 2000 in assam(India).he was started his artist life journey in 2018. his expertise drawing, painting, traveling, blogging and youtuber different types of stage shows make his popularity.

Hi, my name is James. My clients call me "CL" because you cant lose with my mix! I'm a recording and mixing engineer with 6 years of experience. Your sound represents your attitude & Your attitude determines your overall altitude. So let's take take it to the max!

Mixing, Mastering and Editing is the core to every hit song. I've been able to work with the industry's top talent like Black eyed peas, Chris Brown and DJ Snake to name a few. I'm Certified Gold and Platinum and come with 15 years of experience. Let's work together and get some hits!!

3-day guaranteed delivery along with our proven 5-step system for production, mixing and mastering will transform your song to Spotify ready tracks. Grammy nominated producer-engineer duo | 25M+ streams | Former Atlantic Records Engineer. First time clients avail a flat $400 full package deal for production, mixing and mastering.

Hi! I am the vocalist/lyricist in the band "Prinze George". My band has had original music placements on HBO, Freeform and Warner Bros films. I have written/recorded three released tracks with Carnage; one of which Diplo remixed and played it during his set at Coachella last year. Another one features Wiz Khalifa, G-Eazy, and myself singing.

AYDIN HAS BEEN WORKING AS AN ENGINEER - MIXER - PRODUCER WHILE BASED IN LOS ANGELES AREA SINCE 2007. PROFICIENT WITH BOTH LOGIC AND PRO TOOLS SYSTEMS, AYDIN HAS COLLABORATED WITH LIKES OF DIPLO, RICK ROSS, JAMIE JONES (ALL-4-ONE), LUCY GRAVES (BLACK EYED PEAS/CEELO), RAY DE LA GARZA (RED ONE), TIM STEWART (GUITARIST/LADY GAGA/RIHANNA).

Hi everyone, I am a classical and jazz trained pianist/keyboardist. My credits include keyboards, production and musical direction for a number of different artists including work with Statik Selektah, Action Bronson, 2 Chainz, Black Thought, J. Cole, Joey Bada$$, Wiz Khalifa, Freddie Gibbs, Mac Miller (RIP), Duane Mclaughlin,

Steve Banik, professionally known as STACKTRACE, is an American producer, musician, DJ and engineer based in Madison, Wisconsin. Production credits include Nas, Logic, Wiz Khalifa, Russ, Jack Harlow, Method Man and several others. Touring keyboard player, performed on the Tonight Show and Good Morning America.

Credits include Usher, Mary J. Blige, A$AP Rocky, and more. I'm a professional mixer that works on A list clientele. Hit me up and I'll show you how good you can sound!

Black Lotus Music Group is a highly skilled team of mixing and mastering engineers with a keen ear for Pop, Hip Hop, R&B, and Trap music. The founder and head engineer has 10+ years of experience under his belt and has worked with the likes of Wiz Khalifa, Roy Woods, Tyga, and many more. Every member is vetted and has a college degree in audio.

PERFECT YOUR SOUND! Need VOCALS? Need LYRiCS? Need MELODiES? Need help w/ EDiTiNG & MiXiNG a song? I give VOCAL LESSONS! I’m a professional singer-songwriter & producer from Switzerland in LA & will get the best potential out of YOUR song! I have work w/ Jacob Luttrell a multi-Grammy winner, Wiz Khalifa, Jess Jackson, OTG, Tamra Keenan, Jon Ney etc

Grammy nominated producer/engineer/songwriter. Here to help take your emotions, decorate them and make them accessible in a way that others can feel them.

Hi! I am the producer in the band "Prinze George". Along with over 13 million streams on Spotify, I have written songs/recorded three released tracks with Carnage; one of which Diplo remixed and played it during his set at Coachella last year. Another one features Wiz Khalifa and G-Eazy.

JRod thrives at engaging listeners with his soulful, 808-driven approach. Heavily influenced by the likes of producers such as Timbaland, Pharrell, Hit-Boy, Boi-1da & Mike Will Made It, JRod spares no effort in keeping edgy, limitless super-producers alive.

Hey folks! I'm Ryan Matthew Tedder. I'm a producer/songwriter originally from Pittsburgh, PA. An alum of Berklee College, I have produced for Wiz Khalifa, Neyo, Kandi Burruss, T-Pain, Chris Brown, Jennifer Lopez, Lecrae, H.E.R, Ariana Grande, and Meghan Trainor. I signed my first artist Jaira Burns to Interscope records in August of 2016.

I have worked on Chris browns "no guidance" and Indigo album with grammy nominated song writers Robert Norman, Donyea "star child " yeezo. Work closely with Grammy award winner Tommy Brown (Producer of Ariana Grande), Donut (Producer of Ariana Grande). I have gone viral on social media through my singing and influencer videos.

Over 10 years experience.I’ve worked with the industry’s top labels and Grammy winning producers as a mixer. Credits include Stunna4Vegas, Wiz Khalifa, Harry Hudson, ZaZa, Foogiano, Dave East, 24hrs, Danny Towers, Sage The Gemini, Kiing Shooter, Freddie Gibbs, That Girl Lay Lay, Brooklyn Queen, and many more.

I’m a solo artist/session musician who produces and writes songs. I’m into many different vibes and sounds so whatever you do I’m sure I could help take your songs to a better place. I’ve played on recordings by Wiz Khalifa, Rayland Baxter, The Roots, Melody Gardot and others. I love to make a song even better than it was. Let’s make some music!

JV discovered his calling while working behind the scenes as a music producer and mixing engineer at Grammy-award winning production company House Studios. Jake has had the honor to be behind the boards for greats like Faith Evans, Malik Yusef, Ari Lennox, Mannywellz, Wale, B.O.B, Mick Jenkins, 9th Wonder, Jen Miller, Isaiah Thomas and many more.

Need Chubby and Expensive Sounding Mixes? Then you came to the place. I’m here to receive and deliver back to you 100% high quality mixes that will make you fall in love with your song even more.

Accredited Producer, Remixer and Songwriter who has releases and ongoing relationships with Universal Music Group, Sony Music and Warner who has a passion for pop & electronic music that can take your tracks to the next level.

We are Grammy-Award winning Singer-Songwriters, Music Producers, Vocal Arrangers, Concept Consultants, with 10+ yrs experience. We've written for the likes of Chris Brown, Tori Kelly, Diddy, and MIA. We've worked with mega producers, Timbaland, Pop & Oak, Polow Da Don, and Dr. Dre. Now, its time to collaborate with you!

We're a team of producers and songwriters with extensive industry experience. We want to help you create records that you're proud to show your fans and hopefully helps you gain a step forward in your career. For years we've been in the background helping pro artists advance themselves. Now it's your turn!
